    <div class="col-md-2"></div>
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <div class="disclaimer_box">
        <h4 class="text_underline"><strong>Important!</strong></h4>
        <p class="font_italic"><strong>PawBookings.com, Inc. is under no obligation to intervene in any dispute between Users regarding cancellations and/or refunds outside the scope of our cancellation policy. Other terms may apply and pet owners are responsible for reviewing any individual Kennel Operator's policies regarding cancellation fees.</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

